    "description": "Flipkart Logistics Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Supply Chain Manager for our Nashik operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Flipkart Logistics Advisory Limited:\nFlipkart Logistics Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Flipkart Logistics Advisory Limited!",
